\"color: red;\">美國人經常說自己是世界老大，怎麼到這個時候連這點自信都沒有了呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n片：<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=XOZ5_8AEjTc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXOZ5_8AEjTc&d=l9j%2BX5M8xayYNSKzl1ZQhp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=455b49ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=XOZ5_8AEjTc</a>"},{"pid":"bd9f92493d5c32e674a3a584e9f865366d17933d","tid":107883,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T18:08:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://gate.sinovision.net:82/gate/big5/www.sinovision.net/data/attachment/portal/201612/11/121427ji2uio8djmvoou82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgate.sinovision.net%3A82%2Fgate%2Fbig5%2Fwww.sinovision.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fportal%2F201612%2F11%2F121427ji2uio8djmvoou82.jpg&h=b01b6e6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對公眾而言，外交部發言人是了解中國外交政策最直接的窗口。在輿論場上，發言人的一言一行經常成為討論熱點。<br />\n小編梳理了2016年中國外交部十大精彩回應，每一條都相當霸氣，有理有據，有力有節。"},{"pid":"fe35cbb92d4e0c18bb7f3469a79094835cb6b5e4","tid":107883,"uid":74497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T18:09:14.000Z","msg":"你估口交部發言人唔怕比人取消張綠卡咩"},{"pid":"2bb08b1738f77c42e9fb2e1bb59a243f608a6784","tid":107883,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T18:09:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://gate.sinovision.net:82/gate/big5/www.sinovision.net/data/attachment/portal/201612/11/1217059mzkmobs714xsm1x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgate.sinovision.net%3A82%2Fgate%2Fbig5%2Fwww.sinovision.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fportal%2F201612%2F11%2F1217059mzkmobs714xsm1x.jpg&h=d91e03eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8928434733d979929b7c0b741d8fec6ff17aa05","tid":107883,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T04:12:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58dadc